 />\n<br />\n崩壞最出名，地球最強既制作組&nbsp;<br />\n叫座叫賣不突止，又為觀眾著想&nbsp;<br />\n唔鐘意比人劇透？得！有原創劇情&nbsp;<br />\n你又可能會講「屌！d角色崩成咁都唔係人睇既」&nbsp;<br />\n唔緊要，BD已為你準備&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n唔講崩壞方面，又講下佢地劇情方面&nbsp;<br />\n屌啦星！一集廿四分鐘，一集可以講兩本既野 ，對濃縮劇情完全收放自如&nbsp;<br />\n唔留心睇完全唔知劇情做緊乜，就算原作黨點樣不滿&nbsp;<br />\n佢地都一於少理，仲會做到一種好似比原作仲好睇既感覺&nbsp;<br />\n從來唔睇輕小說又想追動畫？唔緊要，去睇節操社<br />\n崩壞，原創，濃縮令到你用24分鐘就好似睇完成套作品咁&nbsp;<br />\n真係十分體貼，請支持J.C.Staff<br />\n<br />\n好節操社，不看嗎？&nbsp;"},{"pid":"708a61840c20ca0ded8e0ec676e0fab013fe6b25","tid":413692,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"咁幾時做"},{"pid":"74742d76045b523fbecd15e35aa8b321b7bdd3d9","tid":413692,"uid":60720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家既JC其實唔差<br />\n但同madhouse一定無得比</blockquote><br />\n睇JC打鬥不如睇PowerPoint&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n依家既jc係好過以前好多<br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">打鬥</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">節奏控制</span>始終都係麻麻<br />\n望佢唔好玩野又大改劇情就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇呢兩樣嘅一拳超人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a884079d8a8997efa25bd36ebaf9596f0d67437d","tid":413692,"uid":41910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家既JC其實唔差<br />\n但同madhouse一定無得比</blockquote><br />\n睇JC打鬥不如睇PowerPoint&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n亞莉亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce4cca29d0107441696561b2c352e533ebfa229","tid":413692,"uid":117333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>依間既打鬥都唔差<br />\n最近一套TABOO TATTOO<img src=\"/assets/faces/